snippet.title: ORBITAL BULLET | Nintendo Switch Reveal Trailer | Pre-Order now!
snippet.description:
Pre-order NOW on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/orbital-bullet-switch/
Releasing November 10!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SmokeStab/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/smokestab/

▬ About Orbital Bullet ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
Kill. Die. Modify. Orbital Bullet is a fast paced 360° action-platformer with rogue-lite elements, where all actions take place in a circular pattern. Fight your way through a variety of procedural planets and use body modifications, crafting and heavy weaponry. #OrbitalBullet #Roguelite
